Hi Marc,

This is the example in the function envfit:

library(vegan)
data(varespec, varechem)
library(MASS)
ord <- metaMDS(varespec)
(fit <- envfit(ord, varechem, perm = 999))
scores(fit, "vectors")
plot(ord)
plot(fit)

